    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>出色的游戏性</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反应灵敏、精准的 2D 游戏，注重增强移动能力。双跳和三跳、墙壁跳跃、传送冲刺和变形。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227320/extras/7edb3f47040274404ecec18e5b6cfd43.poster.avif?t=1755022578\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227320/extras/7edb3f47040274404ecec18e5b6cfd43.webm?t=1755022578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>能力和魔法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一套魔法武器，每种武器都可升级，并有不同的取舍，可通过老式的环形菜单进行选择。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227320/extras/c0871c0438ded5d99e7c46b887bfe79b.poster.avif?t=1755022578\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227320/extras/c0871c0438ded5d99e7c46b887bfe79b.webm?t=1755022578\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>出色的关卡设计</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >六个美丽独特的关卡--探索城堡的众多房间、神秘的矿井或美丽的室外花园！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227320/extras/32d992c7f7bb8bd5389ba297f864a3d7.avif?t=1755022578\" width=620 height=200 /></span>密室、宝箱和藏有传说的石板等着你去发掘。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >带有传送门的快速旅行系统，让回溯更加方便。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2227320/extras/f19458ee7f89ff9aec8308042ac96e3e.avif?t=1755022578\" width=620 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>有意义的角色发展</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有趣的技能树，混合了状态升级、临时 BUFF 和被动技能（如自动治疗和 HP 虹吸）。大量的支线任务、可购买急需药水的商店以及可解锁技能树特殊部分的原料收集系统！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>音乐和音效</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受由 Dynamedion 制作的美妙音乐和音效。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Signiverux 的六个部分中，每个部分都有精心设计的独特音乐。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索、战斗和了解游戏世界奥秘的同时，还能享受到精心设计的音效！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >非常非常感谢</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Andreas Hammann - 音乐作曲家兼音效设计师</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steffen Brinkmann - 音乐作曲家</p>",
